
OUTLINE: 
1. Make essential Imports
2. Initialise engine and set property to voice with speech rate= 170

3. This module will have two functions:
> speak: To only speak
> speakAndGest: To also make hand gestures while speaking corresponding to words said

4. Calculate run time for each speech output file and round it. Write this in JawWS file
5. Wait a given time for jaw syncronisation
6. If speakAndGest is called, then find the apt gesture and write to the Arms file.
7. Say the sentence
8. Remoce the temp file generated for estimating time for jaw
